screen_desc: The screenshot displays a Telegram app interface with a "Log Out" prompt. It asks the user if they are sure they want to log out, explaining that this action will cancel all Secret Chats. There are options to "Cancel" or "Log Out." Below the prompt, there are alternative options to "Add another account" and "Set a Passcode," with brief descriptions of each function. The screen also indicates that logging out will deactivate all Secret Chats.

ui_elements.text: Are you sure you want to log out?This will cancel all your Secret Chats.You can use Telegram on all your devices at once and use several accounts in the same app.
ui_elements.content_desc: "Logout confirmation message explaining the consequences of logging out and mentioning the ability to use Telegram on multiple devices."
